‚úÖ Tip for interview prep:
    For each design question, always structure your response as:
    1.	Requirements ‚Üí functional + non-functional.
    2.	High-level Architecture ‚Üí diagram + service choice (EC2, ECS, Lambda, RDS, etc.).
    3.	Data flow & scaling ‚Üí how traffic and load are handled.
    4.	Security ‚Üí IAM, encryption, VPC, etc.
    5.	Monitoring & Cost Optimization ‚Üí CloudWatch, autoscaling, lifecycle policies.

